content:
Strength:
Clean and Jerk - 15min to find a heavy lift

Metcon:
As many reps as possible in 15min:
2 Hang Power Cleans (#65/45)
2 Pullups
15 Air Squats
4 Hang Power Cleans
4 Pullups
15 Air Squats
6 Hang Power Cleans
6 Pullups
15 Air Squats
etc... adding 2 reps every round to the cleans and pullups.
